        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1383010715" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer773787342076426384">This book was quite good. I had a hard time putting it down. I am always trying to get ahead in life so I totally understand this book. I think it was very well written and worth I read. * I received this book from the author in exchange for an honest review*</span>

